org.twinkql.result.callback
Interface AfterResultBinding<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The callback type
All Superinterfaces:
Callback
public interface AfterResultBinding<T>
extends Callback

A Callback that is fired after the result has been bound to a Java bean. This can be used to add extra information, do post-processing, etc.
